---
description: How to strip demo files and start fresh. Use when the user wants to remove demo content, delete demo, clean up the skeleton, or start from scratch.
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

Read `.claude/rules/reset.md` for the full reset guide — follow every step in order.

Key points: delete `src/app/demo/`, `src/components/demo/`, `src/features/contact/`, `src/features/landing-page/`, related constants, and orphaned public SVGs. Do NOT delete `public/landing-page/` — the root page hero uses those images. Clean translation keys and route constants. Run `pnpm build` to verify after.
